{"tid":1729460,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"癲狗日報：本報攝影師李慶泉，於今日下午在理大外被警方水砲車蓄意射中，本報強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:09:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf9113e24f2e5df96b01ffa016968ab95235785","tid":1729460,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"本報攝影師李慶泉，於今日下午在理大外被警方水砲車蓄意射中，導致頭部和腰部嚴重受傷，現正於伊利沙伯醫院留醫。<br />\n特區政府和香港警察對前綫新聞記者施襲情況無日無之，已經達到令人不能容忍的地步。癲狗日報強烈譴責這種殘害新聞自由及傷害記者人身安全的行為。<br />\n本報保留追究一切傷害本報前綫記者行為的法律及刑事責任的權利。<br />\n<br />\n癲狗日報<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月17日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間16 : 18<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579509036140824?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F198300400928358%2Fposts%2F579509036140824%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=19f87e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579509036140824?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"b451ddfc1a518dea73b96c8a0d35dfe6d6eb2d24","tid":1729460,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"（救Poly)Twitter戰線要人！緊急吹雞！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1729172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1729172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">去將PolyU情況update畀外國政要/外媒/名人有關香港的tweet到</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫推！！！</span>"},{"pid":"336ff46cefe5b6273cfe81c5f6bfca69068778f2","tid":1729460,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579481756143552?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F198300400928358%2Fposts%2F579481756143552%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=bd09cb0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579481756143552?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【兩水炮車漆咸道南射水  疑有記者被射中倒地】<br />\n<br />\n警方派出兩輛水炮車下午2時前，駛至漆咸道南和柯士甸道交界，並向示威者的方向發射藍色和白色水。在理大外集結的示威者未有散去，架起雨傘陣抵擋，並將雜物丟回警方的方向。有記者懷疑被水炮射中倒地，地上看到相信是血跡。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #水炮車"},{"pid":"d9385bc7a37fe3670ae58d089dc61a11d30b2bc1","tid":1729460,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"本報攝影師被魔警水砲車故意直射擊中，頭部和背部嚴重受傷，現正送往伊院作進一步治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579459612812433?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F198300400928358%2Fposts%2F579459612812433%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=9fec5903\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/198300400928358/posts/579459612812433?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"695a8723c579a4c17584eab39b3c8ddb4568283f","tid":1729460,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f74f9071e0acc3a02029dc4fa09762b79123d96","tid":1729460,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa54520d87ee9ea30b3b4ab98301764da8adc96","tid":1729460,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ONpWhA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ONpWhA.png&h=9ffebdb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00a1bc77633e760c9a3005495fbe5a84bee1515","tid":1729460,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TemFoaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTemFoaQ.jpg&h=02bd1e1b&s={SIZE}